{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_14", "eventName": "慈悲燈塔", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "14-2", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "作戰對策會議", "storyInfo": "推進之王收到“灰禮帽”的訊號，得到了關於開斯特公爵的情報。羅德島眾人確認戰場環境後，制定了作戰計畫。\n典範軍與羅德島合作，共同阻止軍事委員會手中的“阿喃那”的徹底降臨。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "50_g25_wildbattlefield_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三小時後"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有發現薩卡茲部隊的蹤跡。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“生命脊椎”目標很大，我們墜落的時候動靜更大，他們趕過來恐怕是遲早的事。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可露希爾小姐，可以確定我們現在的位置嗎？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "可露希爾", "content": "只能根據手上的地圖確認大致方位啦……"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_button", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "可露希爾", "end": "true", "content": "該死，通訊還是毫無反應。", "joined": "只能根據手上的地圖確認大致方位啦……該死，通訊還是毫無反應。"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那具大骨頭摔下來後所有的通訊系統也跟著失靈了，我的無人機都飛不了太遠，這種程度的干擾我以前從來沒遇到過。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#6$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，無人機好像發現了什麼……", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在這邊！", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#5$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "channel": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是什麼？錄音機？", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是，現在的戰場上除了用嘴，也只能用這種方式傳遞訊息了。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#6$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是開斯特公爵的徽記。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看看——", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_button", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_recorderglitch", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "2", "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“滋滋——”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我還有很多事要忙，就直入主題了。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“——劍座。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“……已經抵達銀石崖。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“但銀石崖前線現在的狀況……薩卡茲的手段超出了所有人的預料。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“從西南方向進入戰場，帶上劍——”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“滋——我已經兌現了我的諾言，接下來該……殿下——”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“——滋滋——”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "2"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "43_g1_giantmonstercockpit", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……老樣子，沒什麼起色。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#6$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能不能轉告你那新認識的老伙計，它再不起來幹活的話，我會一根一根掰斷它留下的骨頭架子？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它早就死了，又不知道疼。你想發洩也得找個有意義的對象。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#2$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我們墜落之後，那本來就飄忽不定的聲音更是不再回應任何呼喚。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神經束正在枯萎。什麼手段都試過了，潤滑油，營養劑，連我都沒怎麼聽說過的亂七八糟的巫術。結論就是……", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它現在就是一具沒那麼結實的骸骨，貨真價實。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它該不會是徹底死了吧？死掉的巨獸還會再死一遍嗎？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#4$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊內絲，把那邊骨頭縫裡的雷遞給我。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#4$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……多謝提醒，我差一點就要踩上去了。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以及，你又準備去發什麼瘋？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#10$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我準備聽一下你的建議，找更好炸的對象去。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們那位老相好，不是跟這骨頭架子最熟了嗎？起碼她的肋骨還連著肉，嘴裡也還能吐出像樣的話。她最好能再說點什麼出來。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……厄爾蘇拉。她掌握了許多巨獸相關的秘密，也顯然沒有對我們和盤托出。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但目前的情形恐怕並不是她能解決的。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "問題的源頭……藏在我們頭頂那片紅色的陰雲裡。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#8$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實如此。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，什麼都知道的凱爾希，讓我猜猜看，你又給我們帶來了什麼壞消息？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "普通的天災影響不了巨獸。即便……是已經死去幾百年的這一隻。供它穿行的隧道甚至能夠跨越時間，又怎麼可能因風暴而關閉？", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡發生的事情，已遠非“天災”所能描述。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，墜落的那一刻，我隱約感覺到了。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "骸骨中殘餘的，那古老而巨大的意志……游開了。它去了一個我觸碰不到的地方。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "它真死了？;它自由了？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line124", "option2": "line124"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……它與我們之間的聯繫斷了。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許是暫時的，但時間久了，我們很可能徹底失去對它的掌控。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#2$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的推測是正確的。Logos檢查過了，薩卡茲加諸這具骸骨的巫術正被一股龐大的能量干擾。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#3$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來血魔的儀式確實完成了。赦罪師……奎薩圖什塔正在幫助特雷西斯，實現薩卡茲數千年來都未能做到的事。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（古老的薩卡茲語）“阿喃那”。萬古不愈之創，苦難的搖籃。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多說點能聽懂的，我等著呢。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它是最初的詛咒，也是最初的源石。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這不是傳說中的玩意嗎？赫德雷天天愛看的故事書裡胡編的那種。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#6$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傳說是真實的影子，儘管它已經被塗抹得面目全非。更何況，這傳說來自薩卡茲，甚至是提卡茲。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽起來特雷西斯打算弄個不得了的東西掛在維多利亞頭頂。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#6$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐怕，這也是他選擇倫蒂尼姆作為自己落腳之處的原因。碎片大廈影響天災與源石的能力已足夠成為“阿喃那”的道標。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#2$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在如今的泰拉，它也幾乎只可能在這裡降臨。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說吧，該怎麼拆了它？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……以現在泰拉科技的水準，我們對它無計可施。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#2$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而唯一的好消息是，它還未徹底降臨。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Logos先生，你有什麼發現？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "血魔掌控的那滴血，被他稱為“提卡茲之血”的那一滴……它仍行使著它的職責。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#2$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“阿喃那”之所以能夠跨越萬年歷史，再度降臨，正是因為他的祈願。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#5$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今血的主人已經墜落，但血脈的聯繫依然穩固。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想要阻止“阿喃那”重現於這片大地，我們需要平息血魔的詛咒，令這滴血中包含的怨恨徹底消融。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#2$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想……我可以試試。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與血魔的廝殺沾染了我，影響至今仍未散去，拜此所賜，我能感受到“提卡茲之血”如今脈動的方向。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#5$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它就在食腐者的軍陣後方。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡高機率會是一座赦罪師的祭壇，但突破整個食腐者防線需要付出的時間成本太高了。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我們可以穿越赤鬃山脈，繞開大部分的交戰區。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line180"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "選這條路的風險不會比突破陣線要小。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#3$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "根據觀測報告，赤鬃山脈已經在“阿喃那”的影響下被徹底改造，那裡如今遍布著極端危險的活性化源石。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#3$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但……確實可行。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閃靈已經先我們一步去尋找奎薩圖什塔，順利的話，她也會成為我們的助力。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我支持博士的決定，這確實是最節省時間的方案。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果繼續拖延下去，等到凱爾希醫生口中的“阿喃那”徹底降臨，並被特雷西斯當作戰場上的武器……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們就徹底失去改變局勢的機會了。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕有風險，我們也必須前進。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……W小姐，有件事我需要你的協助。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想找人幫你們守住這骨頭，對吧小兔子？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這具骸骨對我們接下來的行動意義重大。而且，赫德雷先生也很需要它。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從墜落的那一刻起，軍事委員會就無疑盯上了我們。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，好不容易搶來的東西，沒道理那麼輕易還回去。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說個大致時間吧。現在是……下午六點。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_4088_hodrer_1#4$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……三天。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#3$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "周遭的地形已經被完全改變，我們得穿越一片充滿未知危險的荒原。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#3$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "趕路加上一定會遭遇的戰鬥，處理“提卡茲之血”起碼需要三天。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無法移動的骸骨會成為非常顯眼的目標。對你們來說，守住骸骨，未必比之前突襲骸骨輕鬆……", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我建議阿斯卡綸留守“生命脊椎”。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line214"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，我的工作是和你一起行動，並盡力保證你的安全。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那場血魔大君的襲擊中，我的失誤已經讓你負傷。我不希望這樣危險的情況重演。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "“生命脊椎”很重要，基本上由曼弗雷德指揮進攻。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line221"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你很了解他。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line223"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我贊成，薩卡茲在作戰時非常依賴指揮官的臨場判斷。如果能對曼弗雷德進行限制，也許能為雇傭兵分擔一部分壓力。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我尊重你們的決議。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#2$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那幫派不上什麼用場的維多利亞人呢，也和你們一起走嗎？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#4$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們去銀石崖前線。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們，區區幾千個人，裡面還有一堆直到幾個月前都沒摸過武器的好好市民……要去和食腐者大軍打仗？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲，你們有你們的傳說，我們也有我們的。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諸王之息，劈開天災的劍。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然薩卡茲大軍控制了風暴，那也該是這把劍起作用的時候了。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們收到了開斯特公爵的聯絡。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不算聯絡，只是一個邀約。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和我們推測的一樣，薩卡茲的怪東西啟動之後，維多利亞……或者說公爵聯軍遭受了很大的打擊。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開斯特，不，任何大公爵應該都搞清楚了，維多利亞正處在什麼境況中。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都見識過那些冒著紅光，或者其他光的法術祭壇了。目前，倫蒂尼姆外圍戰場，整個都在變成薩卡茲的法陣。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是……薩卡茲式的戰鬥。不是萊塔尼亞式，不是烏薩斯式，不是任何一種我們所熟知的戰術。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“灰禮帽”一定告訴過開斯特了，薩卡茲會讓他們收集的情報變成廢紙。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諸王之息……我手中這根鐵條，不再僅是讓開斯特渴望放到談判桌上的籌碼。它將給戰局帶來切實的、天翻地覆的變化。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰都不知道下一輪天災什麼時候來。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論開斯特的“劍座”是個什麼東西，裝了輪子的方形房子也好，軍官背著的古怪機械也罷，我都會去找到它。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "平息這些風暴，至少能讓戰場重新變得公平些。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從蘇弗里爾峽谷到銀石崖前線，哪怕走公爵們已經清理過的西途林地-吉布森鎮一線，也得花上兩天時間。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以開斯特公爵的手段，只要一有機會，她就會從你手中奪走諸王之息，以期在艱難戰局中統領眾公爵，讓自己距離王座更近一步。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#3$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且會這樣做的，並不只有她一位。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "溫德米爾公爵已經犧牲，她的軍隊也離開了這片戰場。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再有任何一位公爵撤軍，這場戰爭就會變得更艱難，收復倫蒂尼姆的時間就會拖後，因戰爭而死傷的普通人也會更多。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對薩卡茲也好，對維多利亞人也好，這就是決定最終命運的一戰。 ", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#2$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我們……是典範軍。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪裡最需要奇蹟，我們就會去哪裡。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#6$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，如果這把劍真的像傳說中那樣，能令風暴停息，那你們之後去倫蒂尼姆的路，也能更好走些。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可露希爾？", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#3$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#1$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "offsetx": 0.0, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼知道我都準備好了？", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#3$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.0, "offsetx": 0.0, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之呢，你們可靠的首席工程師可露希爾和她的團隊已經研究出了七種抗干擾的通訊方案。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#7$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.0, "offsetx": 0.0, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我部署的設備也已經在分析這場超級天災的趨勢和產生的影響了。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕再劇烈，源石引發的反應也有跡可循，粉塵的濃度啦，活性化的指數啦，還有蔓延的狀態——", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#1$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.0, "offsetx": 0.0, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，這裡恐怕所有的讀數都很高，所以我們沒辦法算出最危險的那些區域會發生什麼。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們能推測出這片戰場上，哪裡相對比較安全。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前提是，我們要更加深入這片戰場的中心，拿到更多的數據才行。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然Misery答應做我們的保鏢啦，但我想，既然大家都要去飛著巫術和炮彈的戰場中心，那我們就是同路。", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#7$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.0, "offsetx": 0.0, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許能勞煩典範軍的各位稍微當一下我們的護衛？", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "義不容辭。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#7$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.0, "offsetx": 0.0, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阻止事情變得更壞，是羅德島的使命，對吧，凱爾希？", "name": "可露希爾"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝你，可露希爾。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……博士。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我和你，還有阿米婭一起走。;我能去幫助推進之王和可露希爾嗎？;我更傾向於留在骸骨這邊。", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line319", "option2": "line325", "option3": "line330"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line337"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許我們這條路是最危險的。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我會確保博士的安全……就和以前每一次一樣。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line337"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，感謝你的信任。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的指揮經驗一定能幫到我們。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#3$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "3"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line337"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這提議是認真的？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小兔子和老女人的寵物不在，我可是想做什麼都能做哦？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#2$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line340"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，你擔心每一位幹員的安危，因而對自己的選擇有些猶豫。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我需要你與我同行。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "和你們一起深入敵後？;去解決那個祭壇？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line347", "option2": "line347"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我們最終要面對之物是確定的。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#2$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“源石”，它塑造了薩卡茲的歷史，也將決定我們每一個人的未來。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許你也曾對羅德島為何會參與這場戰爭心懷疑慮……而過去我並沒有機會解釋，也給不出確切的答案。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我始終懷疑，碎片大廈上空的陰雲裡藏著可怕的東西。當它真的出現在我面前的時候，我依然……百感交集。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#2$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不習慣於探討命運相關的話題，尤其是你和我的“命運”。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是如今，它正在向我們走來。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#5$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "凱爾希……;你的語氣很不同尋常。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line361", "option2": "line361"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#4$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "源石能造成的影響，遠遠超過我們每一個人的認知。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#4$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#4$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "包括你嗎？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line368"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#2$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Dr.{@nickname}……我希望……", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#4$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不，我相信。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你依然是那個能改變一切的人。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我也從來沒有懷疑過。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士……我們該上路了。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "好。;……出發。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line386", "option2": "line386"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用我鳴炮歡送吧？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "W小姐，保重。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……別忘了小兔子，我和那隻羊不一樣，很難死掉。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "典範軍準備好了。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的，推進之王小姐。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諸位，我們都必須抓緊時間了。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這場戰爭中，每一分每一秒……都有人正在因“源石”而受苦。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我們的使命比任何時候都要清晰。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line407"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "阻止源石繼續擴散。;停下“阿喃那”。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line409", "option2": "line409"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，走進陰霾的最深處。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……去倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "炸了那座塔，把最大的混蛋揪出來。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去阻止眼前的……以及未來可能發生的災難。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#13$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {